'From Squeak3.4alpha of 6 November 2002 [latest update: #5109] on 18 November 2002 at 11:14:57 pm'!"Change Set:		fileListFixes-swDate:			18 November 2002Author:			Scott WallaceTwo fixes concerning the registering file-list:¥ If a FileList has a nil directory (as various FileLists used by FileList test-cases seemingly do) do not blow up in #fullName -- instead, use the default directory.¥ Fix up the #testServciesForFileEnding test  to use the default directory."!!FileList methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'sw 11/15/2002 11:07'!fullName	"Answer the full name for the currently selected file."	^ directory		ifNil:			[FileDirectory default fullNameFor: fileName]		ifNotNil:			[directory fullNameFor: fileName]! !!FileListTest methodsFor: 'test' stamp: 'sw 11/13/2002 19:52'!testServicesForFileEnding	"(self selector: #testServicesForFileEnding) debug"	self assert: (self checkIsServiceIsFromDummyTool: 						((FileList new directory: FileDirectory default; yourself) itemsForFile: 'aaa.kkk') first).	self assert:  ((FileList new directory: FileDirectory default; yourself)) isEmpty! !